  "title": "Business Development Assistant (TMP)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Tasks:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Conduct cold calls and outreach to engage prospective clients and generate leads</p></li><li><p>Research industry trends and competitor insights to support business development strategies</p></li><li><p>Gather and consolidate client feedback on platform usage</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Confident communicator (spoken and written)</p></li><li><p>Proactive, resourceful, and well-organised</p></li><li><p>Completed GCE A-Level / Diploma / Degree (any field)</p></li><li><p>Able to commit for a minimum of 3 months</p></li></ul><p><strong>Work Details:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Location: Orchard</p></li><li><p>Working Schedule: Monday to Friday, 8.30am to 5.30pm</p></li></ul><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p>",
