    "uen": "199201634R",
    "description": "<p>HRnet One is the flagship brand of HRnetGroup, the largest Asia-based recruitment agency in Asia Pacific (excluding Japan). Since our founding in Singapore in 1992, we have grown to a network of over 1,000 consultants across 18 cities, dedicated to providing bespoke talent acquisition solutions to our clients.<br>\n<br>\nAt HRnet One, we believe in the power of human connection. We go beyond traditional recruitment to consciously engineer meaningful interactions between exceptional talent and leading organizations. Our approach is built on a deep understanding of our clients' unique needs and a relentless commitment to finding the perfect fit.<br>\n<br>\nWe are a team of passionate, entrepreneurial, and driven individuals. Our success is a result of our purpose-driven work and our commitment to a co-ownership model that aligns our consultants' success with the growth of our company.<br>\n<br>\nIf you are looking to build a career in a dynamic and fast-paced environment where you can make a real impact on people's lives and businesses, HRnet One is the place for you. Join us in shaping the future of work, one connection at a time.</p>",
